overview: "Hip Hop's most notorious groupie." NY Times best selling author "Confessions of a video vixen." "Tell-all" author does it all for the Vivid cameras. She's the New York Times best-selling author of "Confessions of a Video Vixen." She blew the lid off the rap world by exposing her laissons with P. Diddy, Ja Rule, Jay-Z, Usher and more... but before all that, she blew Mr. Marcus and we have the tape to prove it!!! They call her SuperHead... and you're about to find out why...
title: Super Head
